Text: this game was absolutely amazing. This is a 3D flying racer with abilities similar to mariokart. I think there were also stats and powerups you could buy with money from each race. SO awesome.
@Treehugga yeah you're right, that's why I had to upload this game. I also love the commentary before each race. For me Slipstream 5000 is one of the best PC games of the 90s.
